# App purpose :
platform for collecting travel expense reports from employees
the platform is created by an accounting firm called BDO Israel
and it will serve as a tool for the firm's clients (companies) enable the client's employees report their travel expenses

# Main interface :
Company Admin creates trip record with the following data (all mandatory, besides comments):
  departure date
  return date
  trip purpose
  list of names of employees who participated the trip
  list of countries visited
  comments

  after creation : system assigns trip number, prefix + 4digit running number

any user :
  1. log into the system, 
  2. chooses a company (if that user is associated with multiple companies); and 
  3. selects one of the trips of the company he chose at login; and 
  4. add expense details to the trip

  each expense details has the following data:
    date (not mandatory)
    amount
    currency
    description/vendor
    expense type
    employee paid (from company's employees list)


system interface 
  all screens of the system will have BDO logo on it, and will use BDO color scheme (see bdo.co.il)
  
system screens:
  1. login screen
  login with email and password, or google account, or Microsoft account
  after login ,user must choose company, if user is associated with multiple companies

  2. list of trips , with filters, and option to sort by any field, and a search box (+add new trip button for company admin user only)

  3. trip expense report - shows the trip details on the top part of the screen, and on the bottom part the grid for the expenses details
      trip expense report can be finalized
      after trip is finalized it is locked for editing and can only be unlocked by admin user

  4. sys admin :
      new user / edit existing user  
      new company / edit existing company
        for each new company 
          sys admin must associate company admin user (at least one)
          define a prefix for trip numbers (prefix is 3 upper case letters)
      new trip / edit trip details 
      new expense type / disable expense type

  5. company admin :
    new user / edit user (appoint user as admin, or as regular user)
    disable user

  6.  user details:
      first name
      last name
      role (admin / regular)
      login email
      password

  7.  reports
      a. activity log (grid with, date, time, user, activity (only data upates e.g. new trip, new trip expense, not data views)
      b. expense reports to employee (only his expenses in all the trips in all the companies)

